entry.tran: （尤指属于同一社会阶层的）（男）老乡，（男）同乡
entry.def: A homeboy is a boy or man from the same area as you, especially one from the same social group as you.

means.word_mean: 1. a fellow male member of a youth gang
2. a male friend from your neighborhood or hometown
